If it's your raid, you decide if pets are allowed or not.  If it's someone elses, ask before you sign up.  If you're not happy with the answer, don't go.<br>
<br>
And to the Rage of Zomm poster, while I agree with you, I'm not sure if you've used the pet since you said it survives most of the night?  It's a target based pet, it dies when the MOB dies.  The other thing I've found is that the DS on most of those MOBs kills the pet pretty quickly, with or without good taunting.  It would be nice if they upped the total HP on this pet so it could be of some more use.<br>
