1.  Use the Level 55 pet (Rage of Zomm).  Yeah it has crappy HPS.. but it hits for 85 and if you have players tanking the MOB it will deal out considerably damage since it is low taunt.<br>
<br>
2.  Stay back from the action with your met garding near you.  Then engage the MOB.<br>
